      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Node Primitive Consolidation\n\nSeparate the deeper node-architecture questions from interaction policy. This graph is about what a node fundamentally is, what it can contain, and how much of the system truly shares one primitive.",
