    {
      "id": "node-primitive-note-audit",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Initial Audit Findings",
      "position": {
        "x": 1888.8095238095239,
        "y": -156
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Initial Audit Findings\n\nThere is already a real shared substrate, but it is not a single visual primitive.\n\n## Shared across almost everything\n- `useNodePortSchema`\n- absolute positioned node rendering\n- `nodeRefs` registration / measurement conventions\n- event-bus/editor integration\n\n## Document/content family\nMostly composed through `FixedNode` (and `DefaultNode` via `FixedNode`):\n- markdown\n- dictionary\n- legend\n- manifest\n- view\n- div\n- canvas\n- graph-reference\n- port\n- dynamic-view\n- 3d\n\n## Operational/integration family\nMostly bypasses `FixedNode` and hand-rolls its shell/UI:\n- api\n- backgroundRpc\n- counter\n- delay\n- gate\n- script\n- timer\n- toggle\n- valueTrigger\n- svg\n\nThis means the real primitive question is not just `DefaultNode` vs `FixedNode`. It is whether the shared node primitive is visual, behavioral, or both.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
          "nodeDef": {
            "key": "markdown",
            "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
            "source": "local",
            "version": ">=0.1.0"
          },
          "views": [
            {
