      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Capability Model Note\n\nA capability-based node model is a plausible future direction, but it is not yet a settled conclusion.\n\nUse it as a candidate lens while finishing the simpler work first:\n- define the minimal shared contract\n- define node families\n- define composition rules\n\nDo not let the abstraction outrun the codebase.",
