    {
      "id": "node-primitive-plan",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Implementation Plan",
      "position": {
        "x": 512.1428571428573,
        "y": -1326
      },
      "width": 760,
      "height": 280,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Implementation Plan\n\n## Phase 1\n- inventory node families\n- identify outliers\n- write the minimal contract\n\n## Phase 2\n- answer composition questions\n- separate required primitive behavior from optional capabilities\n- make declared ports project cleanly onto node boundaries\n- keep interaction policy as a dependent contract, not the primitive itself\n\n## Phase 3\n- design gradual migration\n- choose first consolidation targets\n- only then begin architectural refactors",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "_classBinding": {
