      "width": 380,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "body": "Goal: Make the node abstraction legible\nStatus: todo\n\nTasks in scope:\n1. Inventory current node families\n2. Define the minimal node contract\n3. Define content, control, and port composition\n4. Project declared ports onto node boundaries\n5. Plan gradual consolidation\n\nOpen questions:\n1. Can every node host content?\n2. Do all nodes actually start from one primitive?\n3. Where does zoom-revealed surface really live?",
        "status": "todo",
        "owner": "Michael",
        "priority": "high",
